---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — AI Tools Nav" description="Learn about AI Tools Nav — who we are, how we test AI tools, and why our reviews are independent.">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 32px; max-width: 740px; margin: 40px auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title">About AI Tools Nav</h1>
    
    <section style="margin: 32px 0;">
      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <strong>AI Tools Nav</strong> is an independent AI tool review platform. 
        We test and evaluate LLMs, image generators, coding assistants, AI voice tools, 
        and every other AI product that promises to change how you work.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Founded in 2024, AI Tools Nav was born from a simple frustration: most "AI tool reviews" 
        are either marketing hype paid for by vendors, or shallow listicles written by people 
        who don't actually use AI in production. We decided to do it differently — every review on this site 
        is written by a practicing developer or AI practitioner who has used the tool in a real workflow.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Our team is small (<strong>5 AI specialists</strong> across time zones), which means every review 
        is meaningful. We don't chase volume — we chase depth. Each review includes hands-on testing, 
        quantitative benchmarks where applicable, and honest pros/cons based on real AI usage patterns.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 32px 0;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Our Review Philosophy</h2>
      <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>No sponsored placements.</strong> Zero. Tools earn their spot on our lists based on merit, not marketing budget.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Real-world AI workflows.</strong> We test tools in actual LLM pipelines, image generation batches, and voice synthesis workloads — not just demos.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Transparent scoring.</strong> Every score comes with a breakdown so you can weigh what matters to your use case.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;"><strong>Living reviews.</strong> We update reviews as AI models evolve. A review from last month may have a new update.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 32px 0;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px;">Contact</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        Questions, suggestions, or tool recommendations? 
        Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@aitoolsnav.net">hello@aitoolsnav.net</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
